
Sorting:  Sorting algorithms that are embedded into a test environment.

SortingAlgorithm: Naked sorting algorithms working on lists and arrays.

SortingAnimation: Animation of various sorting algorithms.

    In order to start the animation, open a terminal in the directory 'SortingAnimation' and
    type the following commands:
    
        Javac *.java
        java AnimationFrame

    The last command should start the Animation.
